          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "12 sectors of the target were produced by",
                "electrodeposition on a 0.62-mg/cm2 Ti backing, were",
                "mounted on a disk 24 cm in diameter, which was",
                "rotated at 980 rpm. To control the thickness of the",
                "target layer during the experiment, about 30 mu-g",
                "of 243Am were added to the target as a marker.",
                "Target thickness was 0.89 mg/cm2 at the energy of 231.1",
                "MeV, 0.76 mg/cm2 at 237.8 MeV and 0.65 mg/cm2 at 250.6",
                "MeV."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "First beam intensity was 4 p mu-A, then it was",
                "reduced to 3 p mu-A."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MAGSP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The reaction products were analyzed by means",
                "of Dubna Gas Filled Recoil Separator (DGFRS-2)."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The focal detector consisted of two 48x128-mm2",
                "double-sided strip detectors with 48 1-mm horizontal",
                "strips on the front side and 128 1-mm-wide vertical",
                "strips on the back one. The first detector shielded a",
                "part of the rear detector. The back strips of 1-mm in",
                "width were paired together to form 110 strips of 2 mm",
                "in width. The focal detector was surrounded by eight",
                "60x120-mm2 side strip detectors, each with 8 strips,",
                "forming box with a depth of 120 mm."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two multiwire proportional chambers were used",
                "to register the nuclei passing through the separator."
              ]
            }
          ],
